      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound 2017 Ford Focus RS, featuring the potent 2.3L EcoBoost power plant equipped with a low-inertia twin-scroll turbocharger. This unit utilizes the Ford Performance All-Wheel Drive system with a GKN Twin-ster rear drive unit, providing dynamic torque vectoring for exceptional lateral grip and neutral handling characteristics. The drivetrain is paired with a short-throw six-speed manual transmission exhibiting precise synchro engagement. Suspension geometry is bolstered by factory-equipped two-mode adjustable dampers and Brembo four-piston fixed front calipers for superior thermal management during spirited driving. The vehicle has been maintained with a strict adherence to oil-change intervals using full synthetic lubricants, and the head gasket recall has been verified and completed. This is a high-performance hatch with a clean powertrain and rigid chassis integrity, ready for immediate deployment.",
