    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi S5 Sportback in Daytona Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between daily utility and exhilarating performance. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the Magma Red Fine Nappa leather S-sport seats are in excellent shape, showing only slight softening of the driver-side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the Audi Virtual Cockpit and the premium Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged V6 runs smoothly, having benefited from regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. The 8-speed Tiptronic transmission shifts crisply, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides rock-solid stability. The car sits on 19-inch Cavo-design wheels with Continental SportContact tires that have roughly 70% tread life remaining. It comes with a complete service history, two key fobs, and a clean title in hand. This is a solid, honest example of a modern performance sedan ready for its next owner.",
